description.content:
Need a professional Full-Stack Web Developer to create a high-performance website that impresses?

You've come to the right place!


I'm a seasoned Full-Stack Web Developer with strong front-end and back-end development skills. Do you need a modern, responsive website, a smooth web app, ai web app or ai API integrations? I'll deliver your vision using clean, scalable, and maintainable code.


What I Provide:

  • Full Frontend & Backend Development
  • Custom Website Development
  • Figma/PSD/XD to Website Conversion
  • Secure REST API Development & Integration
  • E-commerce Functionality & Payment Gateway Setup
  • SEO Optimization & Speed Enhancement
  • Fully Responsive & Mobile-Optimized Design
  • AI integrations chatgpt , deepseek


Tech Stack I Work With:

Frontend:

  • ️ HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
  • ️ React.js, Next.js, Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap
  • ️ GSAP & CSS Animations


Backend:

️ Node.js, Express.js, PHP, Laravel


Databases:

️ MongoDB, MySQL, PostgreSQL


Why Choose Me?

  • 100% Quality Work & Customer Satisfaction
  • Fast & Reliable Communication
  • On-Time Delivery
  • SEO-Friendly & Scalable Code


Let's Talk About Your Project!

Contact me now and get a powerful, custom-built website suited to your business requirements!

questionsAndAnswers.question: How to start order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You can share your designs with me and I will analyze them and send you a quote and timeline, after we finalize, I will send you a custom offer

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you be able to do the backend as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will do only front-end work and I can make forms submissions and other simple things.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What format's you can work on for converting a design into responsive pages?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Figma, PSD, XD, AI, Zeplin, Sketch, PNG or JPG,

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the time frame and cost for one landing page?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will start from $80 for a Good design if the complexity of the design if we have a complex project's price may increase, and the timeline for a simple landing page is 2 day delivery time

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about Revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well, client satisfaction is my responsibility and I will revise the project to your satisfaction.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I have some custom requirements. Can we still proceed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes sure. Just message me in conversation and we will discuss everything. Ultimately, we will develop a website according to your requirements.
